data.text: Worldwide Golf was launched in November 1999. With more than 100 issues to it’s credit Worldwide Golf has become the Middle East’s No.1. Since the launch golf legend Gary Player has been the publication’s Executive Editor and the list of Major champions associated to the publication doesn’t stop there. Both former World No.1’s Greg Norman and Ernie Els express their Major views on the game in their regular monthly columns. As the official publication of The Emirates Golf Federation and The Arab Golf Federation Worldwide Golf not only covers global golf news and features but informs our ever growing readership about Middle East events, promotions and news related articles.
